  {
    "unit": 3,
    "topics": [
      "Cognitive Radio Communications:  capabilities of CR, spectrum sharing models of DSA, basic components of opportunistic  spectrum access,  algorithms  for  DSA,  fundamental  limits  of  cognitive  radios,  mathematical models for networking CRs."
    ]
  },
  {
    "unit": 4,
    "topics": [
      "CR Networks (CRNs): Network coding for CR relay network - system model, assumptions, decode and forward cooperation policy, one-hop relay network, tandem & cooperative relay networks, CRN architecture, terminal architecture of CRN (CR device architecture), QOS provisional diversity radio access networks, scaling laws of CRNs."
    ]
  }
]

